70,"tagline":"Sommeren er varm som somre er flest i Mumidalen: varm og dejlig - og fuld af muligheder...","homepage":"","overview":"Mumitrolden, Snif, Mumrik, Lille My, Snorkfrøken og alle de andre stormulede, underfundige trolde er på den anden ende. En komet er i rasende fart på vej mod Mumidalen! Mumitrolden samler en ekspedition og begiver sig ud på en farefuld rejse mod professorens stjerne-observatorium. Men vil de nå frem i tide? Og vil det lykkes dem at redde alle, før kometen kommer?"},"name":"Dansk","iso_639_1":"da","iso_3166_1":"DK","english_name":"Danish"},{"data":{"title":"Muumipeikko ja pyrstötähti","runtime":70,"tagline":"","homepage":"https://www.moomin.com/","overview":"Tove Janssonin kirjaan perustuva piirroselokuva, jossa Muumipeikko ystävineen lähtee tutkimusmatkalle ja saa kuulla, että maata kohti kiitää pyrstötähti."},"name":"suomi","iso_639_1":"fi","iso_3166_1":"FI","english_name":"Finnish"},{"data":{"title":"Комета в Муминленде","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Знаменитая детская писательница Туве Янссон придумала загадочных существ муминов и их друзей, которые стали знамениты на весь мир. В Долине, где они обитают, все время что-нибудь происходит. Иногда забавное, иногда очень опасное. Вот и сейчас, когда, казалось бы, ничто не предвещало беды, на землю движется Комета из космоса.  Что же будет с Долиной, уютным домиком муминов и всей Землей, если Комета протащит над ней свой пылающий огненно-красный хвост? Еще есть время и можно успеть найти далекую обсерваторию и профессора, который подскажет, как всех спасти."},"name":"Pусский","iso_639_1":"ru","iso_3166_1":"RU","english_name":"Russian"},{"data":{"title":"","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"引っ越してきたばかりのムーミン一家は、ジャコウネズミから地球に迫ってくるという彗星の話を聞く。もっと詳しいことを知るため、ムーミンはミイ、スニフと共に、おさびし山にある天文台へ向かう旅に出る。スナフキン、フローレン、スノークといったおなじみのキャラクターたちとの最初の出会いや襲いかかる怪物や彗星への恐怖と闘いながら仲間たちは旅をつづける。"},"name":"日本語","iso_639_1":"ja","iso_3166_1":"JP","english_name":"Japanese"},{"data":{"title":"Mummitrollet - Kometen kommer","runtime":69,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"En komet er på vei til Mummidalen! Sommeren er som de pleier å være i Mummidalen, varm og hyggelig - og full av muligheter. Men en natt blir det storm, og langt ute i himmelmørket lyser et rødt øye som blir større for hver dag. Det er en komet som kommer nærmere og nærmere mummidalen. Himmelen er rød, havet kryper ned i kulpene, og alle små kryp pakker sakene sine og flykter. Når man er liten, er det vanskelig å forstå at jorden bare er en liten gnist i det store og kullsvarte verdensrommet. For å finne ut mer om kometen, legger Mummitrollet og vennene Sniff og My ut på en spennende ferd til et observatorium, men her finner de ut av ting de helst ikke vil vite..."},"name":"Norsk","iso_639_1":"no","iso_3166_1":"NO","english_name":"Norwegian"},{"data":{"title":"Comet in Moominland","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Italiano","iso_639_1":"it","iso_3166_1":"IT","english_name":"Italian"},{"data":{"title":"Kometa nad Doliną Muminków","runtime":80,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Film animowany oparty na książce szwedzkiej pisarki Tove Jansson. Rodzina baśniowych zwierzątek żyje w pogodnej dolinie. Pewnego dnia odwiedza ich piżmowiec, przedstawiający się jako filozof. Zapowiada wielką katastrofę kosmiczną. Zwierzątka postanawiają odbyć wędrówkę do pobliskiego obserwatorium astronomicznego, by dowiedzieć się prawdy."},"name":"Polski","iso_639_1":"pl","iso_3166_1":"PL","english_name":"Polish"},{"data":{"title":"Die Mumins - Der Komet im Muminland","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Das friedvolle Leben im Mumintal scheint in Gefahr, als plötzlich schwarzer Regen fällt und die Rede von einer Bedrohung aus dem Weltall ist. Um der Sache auf den Grund zu gehen, wollen Mumin und seine Freunde Sniff und Klein Mü die Sternwarte in den einsamen Bergen aufsuchen. Unterwegs treffen sie den klugen Snufkin, der sie begleitet. Tatsächlich stellt sich in der Sternwarte heraus, dass ein Komet auf die Erde zufliegt. Den Kindern bleiben nur zwei Tage Zeit, gemeinsam mit Snufkin ins Mumintal zurückzukehren, um alle Bewohner zu warnen."},"name":"Deutsch","iso_639_1":"de","iso_3166_1":"DE","english_name":"German"},{"data":{"title":"Mumintrollet & hans vänner - \"Kometen kommer\"","runtime":73,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Det är sommar i den vackra Mumindalen. Här njuter Mumintrollet och hans vänner Sniff, Lilla My, Snusmumriken och Snorkfröken. Men långt borta syns något okänt och skimrande på himlen. För att ta reda på vad det mystiska fenomenet betyder ger sig vännerna iväg på en strapatsrik färd till ett observatorium i bergen."},"name":"svenska","iso_639_1":"sv","iso_3166_1":"SE","english_name":"Swedish"},{"data":{"title":"המומינים: כוכב השביט","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"כשמר מושקר מצביע על אסון קרב - כוכב שביט שעומד ליפול על העמק ולהחריב אותו, מומינטרול, מאי הקטנה, וסניף עוזבים את עמק המומינים למצפה הכוכבים הישן, בדרך הם פוגשים לראשונה את סנופקין ומס' מדענים שמספרים להם שעליהם לחזור לעמק לפני שהשביט יפול, בדרך הם פוגשים את הסנורקים - סנורק וסנורקה, ואת מר המיולין. יחד עם מומינאבא ומומינאמא, כולם יוצאים למערה כדי להתגונן מהשביט."},"name":"עִבְרִית","iso_639_1":"he","iso_3166_1":"IL","english_name":"Hebrew"},{"data":{"title":"Kometa Mumių šalyje","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Sužinojęs, apie pro šalį skriesiančią kometą, Muminukas su savo draugu Snifu iškeliauja į Observatoriją Vienišuosiuose Kalnuose pasitarti su Profesoriais. Kelyje jie patiria gausybę nuotykių. Tačiau rimčiausias išbandymas lauks paaiškėjus, kad kometa skrieja tiesiai į mylimąjį Mumių Slėnį."},"name":"Lietuvių","iso_639_1":"lt","iso_3166_1":"LT","english_name":"Lithuanian"},{"data":{"title":"Muumitroll ja Sabatäht","runtime":0,"tagline":"Seiklus, millest kõik algas","homepage":"","overview":"Kui Muumitroll saab teada, et Maast on lähedalt möödumas sabatäht, lähevad nad koos Sniffiga Üksiku Mäe observatooriumisse professoritega konsulteerima. Teel on neil mitmeid seiklusi, aga kõige suurem seiklus ootab neid ees siis, kui nad saavad teada, et komeet liigub täpselt nende kallisse Muumiorgu."},"name":"Eesti","iso_639_1":"et","iso_3166_1":"EE","english_name":"Estonian"},{"data":{"title":"姆明一族 冒险日记","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"普通话","iso_639_1":"zh","iso_3166_1":"CN","english_name":"Mandarin"},{"data":{"title":"Mummitrollet - Kometen Kommer","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"En komet er på vei til Mummidalen! Sommeren er som de pleier å være i Mummidalen, varm og hyggelig - og full av muligheter. Men en natt blir det storm, og langt ute i himmelmørket lyser et rødt øye som blir større for hver dag. Det er en komet som kommer nærmere og nærmere mummidalen. Himmelen er rød, havet kryper ned i kulpene, og alle små kryp pakker sakene sine og flykter. Når man er liten, er det vanskelig å forstå at jorden bare er en liten gnist i det store og kullsvarte verdensrommet. For å finne ut mer om kometen, legger Mummitrollet og vennene Sniff og My ut på en spennende ferd til et observatorium, men her finner de ut av ting de helst ikke vil vite..."},"name":"Bokmål","iso_639_1":"nb","iso_3166_1":"NO","english_name":"Norwegian Bokmål"},{"data":{"title":"Halastjarnan kemur","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":""},"name":"Íslenska","iso_639_1":"is","iso_3166_1":"IS","english_name":"Icelandic"},{"data":{"title":"Mumínci ve filmu: Kometa se blíží","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Mumínci žili spokojeně a šťastně ve svém údolí, dokud se jednoho dne neobjevila na nebu zářivá kometa, která se má brzy srazit se Zemí. Mumínci proto pospíchají domů připravit se... Přidejte se k nim v zábavném a napínavém dobrodružství s nečekaným koncem!"},"name":"Český","iso_639_1":"cs","iso_3166_1":"CZ","english_name":"Czech"},{"data":{"title":"Komēta nāk","runtime":0,"tagline":"","homepage":"","overview":"Kad trollītis Mumins uzzina, ka tuvojas komēta, viņš kopā ar savu draugu Snifu dodas uz Vientuļo kalnu observatoriju, lai aprunātos ar zinātniekiem. Viņus gaida dažādi piedzīvojumi, bet lielākais pārsteigums ir ziņa, ka komēta lido tieši uz Muminieleju."},"name":"Latviešu","iso_639_1":"lv","iso_3166_1":"LV","english_name":"Latvian"}],"reviews_tmdb":[],"recommendations":[{"id":788734,"adult":false,"title":"Sick of Myself","video":false,"overview":"Increasingly overshadowed by her boyfriend's recent rise to fame as a contemporary artist creating sculptures from stolen furniture, Signe hatches a vicious plan to reclaim her rightfully deserved attention within the milieu of Oslo's cultural elite.","genre_ids":[18,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.867,"vote_count":378,"poster_path":"/ynePU5z7JFn2Gf82RmfZgV84H8X.jpg","release_date":"2022-09-30","vote_average":7.187,"backdrop_path":"/lk0R4K0kXH8zORA8JWDxqgYLNvJ.jpg","original_title":"Syk pike","original_language":"no"},{"id":34746,"adult":false,"title":"Death Wish V: The Face of Death","video":false,"overview":"Paul Kersey is back at working vigilante justice when his fiancée, Olivia, has her business threatened by mobsters.","genre_ids":[28,80,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":1.0127,"vote_count":296,"poster_path":"/5gcpHxQh93M6CKTIMpngErxxq0D.jpg","release_date":"1994-01-14","vote_average":5.6,"backdrop_path":"/tZGsjeXFg0hRv0Uip2cQJ8fxX3Y.jpg","original_title":"Death Wish V: The Face of Death","original_language":"en"},{"id":33838,"adult":false,"title":"The Care Bears Adventure in Wonderland","video":false,"overview":"The cuddly Care Bears and their cousins star in this charming third feature-length film incorporating characters from Alice in Wonderland. A young girl named Alice and the Care Bears travel together into the whimsical land of the Mad Hatter and the Cheshire Cat. In this magical story about friendship and self-esteem, they try to thwart an evil wizard's attempt to become the King of Wonderland.","genre_ids":[10751,16],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.3429,"vote_count":35,"poster_path":"/yRuyXsh8aMXt95Mjj2Gaj9zADwb.jpg","release_date":"1987-08-07","vote_average":5.8,"backdrop_path":"/10YAxPbDVrB00oBWC5OExNGiBRr.jpg","original_title":"The Care Bears Adventure in Wonderland","original_language":"en"},{"id":58704,"adult":false,"title":"The Wonderful World of Puss 'n Boots","video":false,"overview":"His goal is to help the weak and defenseless, but his saving a mouse makes him the most wanted in all the land. On the run from incessant, dim-witted mice, Perro befriends a young miller's boy, Pierre; together, they decide to seek fame and fortune. When they cross paths with the lovely Princess Rosa, Perro determines to get Pierre hitched to Her Royal Highness.","genre_ids":[10751,28,12,35,16],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.6603,"vote_count":33,"poster_path":"/6TM68raRJOgfdyrlmToIjh8lHRs.jpg","release_date":"1969-03-18","vote_average":7,"backdrop_path":"/jyzBfB9aRoBhQ4lqnauGGsAKeG8.jpg","original_title":"長靴をはいた猫","original_language":"ja"},{"id":124215,"adult":false,"title":"Bamses Gemme-æske","video":false,"overview":"Bamse has dug up some of his all-time favorite moments from the archives. Over 5 hours of entertainment collected on 6 DVDs in Bamse's treasure chest. Some things never go out of style: good weather, delicious food, cute kids, and Bamse and Kylling... It was 1982 when Bamse first appeared on Danish TV. Bamse has many friends, but his two closest are Kylling and Ælling. The trio loves to go on new adventures, but Bamse prefers to decide how things should be done. These are the first six Bamse DVDs collected in the \"treasure box.\" Five hours of wonderful and fun entertainment for the little ones. The treasure box contains the following episodes: - Dangerous Fly Agaric Mushrooms - Luna's Dream Journey - Sven Herlig and Dorthe-Elisabeth! - Troublesome Fog - Swimming Lessons - Laundry Day - Duckling Visits - Baby Chick - Strong Bamse - Askes' Working Drawing - Hungry Bamse - Baking Day","genre_ids":[],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.0695,"vote_count":1,"poster_path":null,"release_date":"2006-01-01","vote_average":8,"backdrop_path":null,"original_title":"Bamses Gemme-æske","original_language":"da"},{"id":1226095,"adult":false,"title":"Les Scandales de « La Religieuse »","video":false,"overview":"Released in 1796 posthumously, The Nun, a novel that Diderot did not dream of publishing during his lifetime, as he knew it to be revolutionary, caused the same explosion in the 19th century France as in that of the 1960s, when Jacques Rivette decided to adapt it, with Anna Karina in the title role. “This film is banned and it will remain so!” said the General de Gaulle. Exploration of an indictment of incredible modernity which, through the tragedy of the young Suzanne, locked up in the convent against her will, denounces the inequity of a society denying women all moral, political and sexual freedom.","genre_ids":[99],"media_type":"movie","popularity":0.1721,"vote_count":3,"poster_path":"/p5530WxQKKxz3QwU8yjNaRHtlL6.jpg","release_date":"2023-11-08","vote_average":8,"backdrop_path":"/5MKTEOGF0fmnjWPSjoEIDXRiIc1.jpg","original_title":"Les Scandales de « La Religieuse »","original_language":"fr"},{"id":16859,"adult":false,"title":"Kiki's Delivery Service","video":false,"overview":"A young witch, on her mandatory year of independent life, finds fitting into a new community difficult while she supports herself by running an air courier service.","genre_ids":[16,10751,14,18],"media_type":"movie","popularity":6.2807,"vote_count":4462,"poster_path":"/Aufa4YdZIv4AXpR9rznwVA5SEfd.jpg","release_date":"1989-07-29","vote_average":7.83,"backdrop_path":"/h5pAEVma835u8xoE60kmLVopLct.jpg","original_title":"魔女の宅急便","original_language":"ja"},{"id":10020,"adult":false,"title":"Beauty and the Beast","video":false,"overview":"Follow the adventures of Belle, a bright young woman who finds herself in the castle of a prince who's been turned into a mysterious beast. With the help of the castle's enchanted staff, Belle soon learns the most important lesson of all -- that true beauty comes from within.","genre_ids":[10749,10751,16,14],"media_type":"movie","popularity":10.8508,"vote_count":10519,"poster_path":"/hUJ0UvQ5tgE2Z9WpfuduVSdiCiU.jpg","release_date":"1991-10-22","vote_average":7.724,"backdrop_path":"/fW4ZCoEZRBqLAJGFQ2g5AdAfPQR.jpg","original_title":"Beauty and the Beast","original_language":"en"},{"id":597,"adult":false,"title":"Titanic","video":false,"overview":"101-year-old Rose DeWitt Bukater tells the story of her life aboard the Titanic, 84 years later. A young Rose boards the ship with her mother and fiancé. Meanwhile, Jack Dawson and Fabrizio De Rossi win third-class tickets aboard the ship. Rose tells the whole story from Titanic's departure through to its death—on its first and last voyage—on April 15, 1912.","genre_ids":[18,10749],"media_type":"movie","popularity":28.4976,"vote_count":26828,"poster_path":"/9xjZS2rlVxm8SFx8kPC3aIGCOYQ.jpg","release_date":"1997-12-18","vote_average":7.903,"backdrop_path":"/xnHVX37XZEp33hhCbYlQFq7ux1J.jpg","original_title":"Titanic","original_language":"en"},{"id":11324,"adult":false,"title":"Shutter Island","video":false,"overview":"World War II soldier-turned-U.S. Marshal Teddy Daniels investigates the disappearance of a patient from a hospital for the criminally insane, but his efforts are compromised by troubling visions and a mysterious doctor.","genre_ids":[18,53,9648],"media_type":"movie","popularity":14.6244,"vote_count":25460,"poster_path":"/nrmXQ0zcZUL8jFLrakWc90IR8z9.jpg","release_date":"2010-02-14","vote_average":8.2,"backdrop_path":"/8xt8AMb1OKC63AdhNSaYBWxB4Iq.jpg","original_title":"Shutter Island","original_language":"en"},{"id":13510,"adult":false,"title":"Eden Lake","video":false,"overview":"When a young couple goes to a remote wooded lake for a romantic getaway, their quiet weekend is shattered by an aggressive group of local kids. Rowdiness quickly turns to rage as the teens terrorize the couple in unimaginable ways, and a weekend outing becomes a bloody battle for survival.","genre_ids":[27,53],"media_type":"movie","popularity":4.608,"vote_count":2024,"poster_path":"/tOg6ElTe1mJwaCFN0172U4oso22.jpg","release_date":"2008-09-12","vote_average":6.832,"backdrop_path":"/s9v1QZMVhwShQ7415jPhtfqzyjG.jpg","original_title":"Eden Lake","original_language":"en"},{"id":65,"adult":false,"title":"8 Mile","video":false,"overview":"For Jimmy Smith, Jr., life is a daily fight just to keep hope alive. Feeding his dreams in Detroit's vibrant music scene, Jimmy wages an extraordinary personal struggle to find his own voice - and earn a place in a world where rhymes rule, legends are born and every moment… is another chance.","genre_ids":[18,10402],"media_type":"movie","popularity":5.7383,"vote_count":7690,"poster_path":"/7BmQj8qE1FLuLTf7Xjf9sdIHzoa.jpg","release_date":"2002-11-08","vote_average":7.14,"backdrop_path":"/jNG7pl0DkN1nzxnbZj4MCGf2VEG.jpg","original_title":"8 Mile","original_language":"en"},{"id":297222,"adult":false,"title":"PK","video":false,"overview":"A stranger in the city asks questions no one has asked before. Known only by his initials, the man's innocent questions and childlike curiosity take him on a journey of love, laughter and letting go.","genre_ids":[35,18,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":6.4022,"vote_count":1122,"poster_path":"/z2x2Y4tncefsIU7h82gmUM5vnBJ.jpg","release_date":"2014-12-18","vote_average":7.698,"backdrop_path":"/gxfvtq5eYiClS2X7hxAAPBNrbWA.jpg","original_title":"पीके","original_language":"hi"},{"id":105,"adult":false,"title":"Back to the Future","video":false,"overview":"Eighties teenager Marty McFly is accidentally sent back in time to 1955, inadvertently disrupting his parents' first meeting and attracting his mother's romantic interest. Marty must repair the damage to history by rekindling his parents' romance and - with the help of his eccentric inventor friend Doc Brown - return to 1985.","genre_ids":[12,35,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":18.5525,"vote_count":21421,"poster_path":"/vN5B5WgYscRGcQpVhHl6p9DDTP0.jpg","release_date":"1985-07-03","vote_average":8.324,"backdrop_path":"/qskzmLTbarKnXDbo2HRj4NJ3vcW.jpg","original_title":"Back to the Future","original_language":"en"},{"id":11158,"adult":false,"title":"Honey, I Blew Up the Kid","video":false,"overview":"Wayne Szalinski is at it again. But instead of shrinking things, he tries to make a machine that can make things grow. As in the first one, his machine isn't quite accurate. But when he brings Nick & his toddler son Adam to see his invention, the machine unexpectedly starts working. And when Adam comes right up to the machine, he gets zapped along with his stuffed bunny.","genre_ids":[12,35,10751,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":2.4763,"vote_count":1251,"poster_path":"/4EGqDo2pP2ZL0TCcYDGnwsU8liQ.jpg","release_date":"1992-07-16","vote_average":5.273,"backdrop_path":"/r4Vx7kne6dovybAJR4LsR4eQCxP.jpg","original_title":"Honey, I Blew Up the Kid","original_language":"en"},{"id":1893,"adult":false,"title":"Star Wars: Episode I - The Phantom Menace","video":false,"overview":"Anakin Skywalker, a young slave strong with the Force, is discovered on Tatooine. Meanwhile, the evil Sith have returned, enacting their plot for revenge against the Jedi.","genre_ids":[12,28,878],"media_type":"movie","popularity":8.0481,"vote_count":15574,"poster_path":"/6wkfovpn7Eq8dYNKaG5PY3q2oq6.jpg","release_date":"1999-05-19","vote_average":6.6,"backdrop_path":"/3TeGmKJfkik1D1rIoqGb1aR4k9c.jpg","original_title":"Star Wars: Episode I - The Phantom Menace","original_language":"en"},{"id":1370,"adult":false,"title":"Rambo III","video":false,"overview":"Combat has taken its toll on Rambo, but he's finally begun to find inner peace in a monastery. When Rambo's friend and mentor Col. Trautman asks for his help on a top secret mission to Afghanistan, Rambo declines but must reconsider when Trautman is captured