arious wizard Saruman awaits the Fellowship members at the Orthanc Tower in Isengard.","genre_ids":[12,14,28],"popularity":17.7989,"vote_count":23477,"poster_path":"/5VTN0pR8gcqV3EPUHHfMGnJYN9L.jpg","release_date":"2002-12-18","vote_average":8.413,"backdrop_path":"/kWYfW2Re0rUDE6IHhy4CRuKWeFr.jpg","original_title":"The Lord of the Rings: The Two Towers","original_language":"en"},{"id":122,"adult":false,"title":"The Lord of the Rings: The Return of the King","video":false,"overview":"As armies mass for a final battle that will decide the fate of the world--and powerful, ancient forces of Light and Dark compete to determine the outcome--one member of the Fellowship of the Ring is revealed as the noble heir to the throne of the Kings of Men. Yet, the sole hope for triumph over evil lies with a brave hobbit, Frodo, who, accompanied by his loyal friend Sam and the hideous, wretched Gollum, ventures deep into the very dark heart of Mordor on his seemingly impossible quest to destroy the Ring of Power.​","genre_ids":[12,14,28],"popularity":23.6525,"vote_count":26076,"poster_path":"/rCzpDGLbOoPwLjy3OAm5NUPOTrC.jpg","release_date":"2003-12-17","vote_average":8.494,"backdrop_path":"/2u7zbn8EudG6kLlBzUYqP8RyFU4.jpg","original_title":"The Lord of the Rings: The Return of the King","original_language":"en"},{"id":123,"adult":false,"title":"The Lord of the Rings","video":false,"overview":"Young Hobbit Frodo Baggins is thrown into an amazing adventure when he's tasked with destroying the One Ring, created by the dark lord Sauron. Frodo must travel in a small fellowship of nine warriors and accomplices. But it won't be an easy journey for the Fellowship of the Ring, on the ultimate quest to rid Middle-earth of evil.","genre_ids":[12,16,14],"popularity":2.9408,"vote_count":1023,"poster_path":"/liW0mjvTyLs7UCumaHhx3PpU4VT.jpg","release_date":"1978-11-15","vote_average":6.6,"backdrop_path":"/TXSxV23MWYkezZ3219gtgcSX6n.jpg","original_title":"The Lord of the Rings","original_language":"en"},{"id":128,"adult":false,"title":"Princess Mononoke","video":false,"overview":"Ashitaka, a prince of the disappearing Emishi people, is cursed by a demonized boar god and must journey to the west to find a cure. Along the way, he encounters San, a young human woman fighting to protect the forest, and Lady Eboshi, who is trying to destroy it. Ashitaka must find a way to bring balance to this conflict.","genre_ids":[12,14,16],"popularity":10.3878,"vote_count":8783,"poster_path":"/cMYCDADoLKLbB83g4WnJegaZimC.jpg","release_date":"1997-07-12","vote_average":8.324,"backdrop_path":"/gl0jzn4BupSbL2qMVeqrjKkF9Js.jpg","original_title":"もののけ姫","original_language":"ja"},{"id":129,"adult":false,"title":"Spirited Away","video":false,"overview":"A young girl, Chihiro, becomes trapped in a strange new world of spirits. When her parents undergo a mysterious transformation, she must call upon the courage she never knew she had to free her family.","genre_ids":[16,10751,14],"popularity":19.9791,"vote_count":17993,"poster_path":"/39wmItIWsg5sZMyRUHLkWBcuVCM.jpg","release_date":"2001-07-20","vote_average":8.533,"backdrop_path":"/ukfI9QkU1aIhOhKXYWE9n3z1mFR.jpg","original_title":"千と千尋の神隠し","original_language":"ja"}],"external_ids":{"imdb_id":"tt0240425","twitter_id":null,"facebook_id":null,"wikidata_id":"Q1779921","instagram_id":null,"mydramalist_id":"34717"},"social_ids":{"twitter":null,"facebook":null,"instagram":null},"gdvg_id":148516,"wiki_plot":null,"wiki_synopsis":null,"wiki_episode_guide":null,"wiki_production":null,"wiki_cast_notes":null,"wiki_reception":null,"wiki_soundtrack":null,"wiki_release":null,"wiki_accolades":null,"release_dates":[{"iso_3166_1":"DK","release_dates":[{"note":"","type":3,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"1995-11-03T00:00:00.000Z","certification":""}]},{"iso_3166_1":"FI","release_dates":[{"note":"","type":3,"iso_639_1":"","descriptors":[],"release_date":"1993-04-02T00:00:00.000Z","certification":"S"}]},{"iso_3166_1":"JP","release_dates":[{